    "His parents were Gabriel Rosenberg and Bertha Rosenbaum (Rosenberg).": [],
    "Early in his life, Rosenberg planned to entry his family's antique business.": [],
    "However, when World War I was declared, he joined the German army cavalry and during a campaign in France, was wounded, captured and sent to a POW camp in Scotland.": [],
    "In a prisoner exchange, Rosenberg was sent to Switzerland where he was allowed to study art history initially at Bern and later Z\u00fcrich.": [],
    "After the war he apprenticed with an art dealer, however, his temperament, by his own admission was more toward scholarship than trade.": [],
